snippet.title: Christa Horath
snippet.description:
Hi! My name is Christa and I'm a stay at home mom of 2 from Central California! I post videos every Monday, Wednesday and Friday all about motherhood, lifestyle, day in the life vlogs and everything in between. My goal is to encourage authenticity and REALNESS by sharing the up's and down's of this beautiful life! I'm so grateful to have each and everyone of you! XO
